        "$cosθ = n1 * n2 / |n1| X |n2|$\n",
        "\n",
        "n1​​=(1,1,1)\n",
        "\n",
        "n2​​=(1,0,0)\n",
        "\n",
        "n1​​⋅n2​​=(1)(1)+(1)(0)+(1)(0)=1\n",
        "\n",
        "∣n1​​∣= $\\sqrt{1^2+1^2+1^2}$ = $\\sqrt{3}$\n",
        "\n",
        "∣n2∣= $\\sqrt{1^2+0%2+0^2}$ = 1\n",
        "\n",
        "$cosθ = n_1 * n_2 /|n_1||n_2| = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}}$\n",
